### 模板定义
使用 `[templates.template_name]` 定义可复用的字段模板：
```toml
[templates.create_update_time]
export_path = "common.mixins"  # 可选：导出路径
columns = [
    {name = "created_at", type = "datetime", comment = "创建时间"},
    {name = "updated_at", type = "datetime", comment = "更新时间"},
]
```

### 实体定义
使用 `[entities.EntityName]` 定义实体：
```toml
[entities.USER]
extends = ["create_update_time", "enable"]  # 继承模板（数组格式）
comment = "用户实体"
columns = [
    {name = "id", type = "int", is_pk = true, comment = "主键"},
    {name = "username", type = "string", unique = true, comment = "用户名"},
]
```

### 关系定义
